cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically human pose estimation from a single image. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category. The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of 3D human skeletons suggests that the paper could also be categorized under cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
